author: Bikash Singh
title: COVID-19: A mobility start-up in Assam develops a mobile app "STAY HOME"
description: Financial institution, North Eastern Development Finance Corporation Ltd (NEDFi) has extended venture funding to this group.
content:
GUWAHATI: A mobility start-up in Assam, ParkingRhino has developed a mobile app "STAY HOME" to track home quarantine people to reduce the spread of the COVID19 pandemic.
